Content:
Elon - are you able to access your Twitter account ok ? I saw a number of emails held in spam .
Including some password resets attempts
I haven't tried recently
Am staying off twitter
Is my twitter account posting anything ?

Not posting but I see one deactivation email and a dozen password reset emails . Assuming
this is a scammer attempt but wanted to check to ensure you still had access to your Twitter
It is someone trying to hack my twitter
But I have two - factor enabled with the confirmation app
OK , great to hear .

Yes - FaceTimed with them to confirm my identity ( hah ) and they are hopefully gonna reset
your ZFA to SMS soon . Asking for an update now
Sounds good
I can also FaceTime with them if still a problem

Tldr ; your account is considered high profile internally over there . So they've made it very
hard to make changes like this by their teams . They are working through it ....
Happy to FaceTime directly

Not sure how I was able to make Twitter work on this new phone , as I didn't use the backup
code .
Connecting with their head of Trust & Safety now
I assume we used your old phone to verify the new , once upon a time
Oh yeah

They can fix it by disabling all 2FA for your account which will let you in and then you can re
enable it . Are you available in 90 mins to have them coordinate it ?

Liked " They can fix it by disabling all 2FA for your account which will let you in and then you
can re - enable it . Are you available in 90 mins to have them coordinate it ? "

I know things are in flux right now , but is EMDesk SpaceX still your primary calendar ? I realize
there a meeting on there in 1 hour . In case I should move this twitter fix out a bit .
Yeah
But I can step off the call briefly to FaceTime them if need be

Sounds good . And ideally I'm just texting you to sign in once they disable 2FA and then you
can immediately sign in and re - enable . No FaceTime needed .

Liked " Sounds good . And ideally I'm just texting you to sign in once they disable 2FA and then
you can immediately sign in and re - enable . No FaceTime needed . "
Elon- we are ready to make the change if you are
Liked " Elon - we are ready to make the change if you are "
2FA disabled . Please try to log in now
Able to get back in ok ?
Liked " Able to get back in ok ? "
And once in you can enable 2FA Settings > Security and account access > Security > 2FA
App only is suggested
Thanks !
And reminder to save that backup code
